*Soja, Edward W. 1996. ''Thirdspace: Journeys to Los Angeles and Other Real-And-Imagined Places''. Wiley-Blackwell. {{ISBN|1-55786-675-9}}
*[[Yi-Fu Tuan|Tuan, Yi Fu]]. 1977. ''Space and Place: The Perspective of Experience''. Minneapolis: University of Minnesota Press. {{ISBN|0-8166-3877-2}}
*[[Yi-Fu Tuan|Tuan, Yi Fu]]. 1990. ''[[Topophilia]]: A Study of Environmental Perception, Attitudes and Values''. New York: Columbia University Press. {{ISBN|0-231-07395-X}}

